summary: "Final Destination 2" is a 2003 horror movie, the second in the series. A woman, A.J. Cook, has a vision of a deadly car crash and saves herself and others. Death comes after them, trying to claim their lives. It's directed by David R. Ellis and stars Ali Larter. Filming happened in Canada. The movie made around $90 million worldwide but got mixed reviews. A third film followed in 2006.
title: Final Destination 2
